The term '''Nessies''' was used to refer to the twenty-five native [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] populations of the [[Star system/Legends|system]] [[Stenness Node]], a group of [[Mining/Legends|mining]] [[Planet/Legends|worlds]] in the [[Inner Rim/Legends|Inner Rim]] The Nessies operated the mines in the region and traded with outworlders. They also used [[Ithullan ore hauler|Ithullian ore haulers]], which were made from the carapaces of the colossus wasps of [[Ithull]].<ref name="FF11">{{FactFile|11|PLA 7-8|Planets of the Inner Rim}}</ref>

